#: data/io.github.pawanrai9999.respite.metainfo.xml.in:10
msgid ""
"Respite helps you protect your eyes, posture, and focus by enforcing regular "
"breaks while you work. You set how long you want to work and how long each "
"break should last, and Respite takes care of the rest."
msgstr ""

#: data/io.github.pawanrai9999.respite.metainfo.xml.in:15
msgid ""
"When the work interval elapses, Respite blacks out every monitor with a "
"centered countdown until the break is over. Breaks are not infinitely "
"dismissible: a limited, configurable number of postponements lets you delay "
"an urgent moment without skipping breaks entirely."
msgstr ""

